{"lemma":"رُمَّة","slug":"رُمَّة","root":"ر.م.م","root_slug":"ر-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16559","n16568","n16569"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cadaver"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/rim.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16559","headword_ar":"رَمَّهُ","root":"rm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarum~u","text_ar":"يَرُمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarim~u","text_ar":"يَرِمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) the latter [irreg. as aor. of a trans. v. of this class, and] said by MF to be unknown, but there are other instances of the same kind, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"har~ahu","text_ar":"هَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yahur~u","text_ar":"يَهُرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yahir~u","text_ar":"يَهِرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~ahu","text_ar":"عَلَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEul~u","text_ar":"يَعُلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEil~u","text_ar":"يَعِلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~N","text_ar":"رَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maram~apN","text_ar":"مَرَمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, T, S, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put it into a good, sound, right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper, state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, Mgh, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after a part thereof had become in a bad state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T;) namely, a thing, (Lth, T, S,) as, for instance, a rope becoming old and worn-out, or a house, (Lth, T,) or a building, (Mgh,) or a wall, &c.; (Msb;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~a $aA^onahu","text_ar":"رَمَّ شَاْنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aA^onahaA","text_ar":"شَاْنَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"referring to a house ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAr","text_ar":"دَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Lth, T:) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he rectified it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, an affair,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after it had become disorganized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disordered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rm~m","text_ar":"رمّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same in an intensive sense; [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repaired it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramorama","text_ar":"رَمْرَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repaired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rectified, his affair, case, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) The saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA A^ahola vam~ihi waram~ihi","text_ar":"كُنَّا اَهْلَ ثَمِّهِ وَرَمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,) occurring in a trad., (S,) accord. to the relaters thereof ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~ihi warum~ihi","text_ar":"ثُمِّهِ وَرُمِّهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", but A'Obeyd holds the former reading to be the right, (T, S,) means, accord. to AA,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were the fit persons to put it into a good, sound, right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper, state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or, accord. to A'Obeyd,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to put it into such a state, and to eat it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S. [See another explanation of the verb in what follows.]) ―         -b2-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~a sahomahu","text_ar":"رَمَّ سَهْمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made his arrow even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straight, by means of his eye;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he looked at his arrow until he made it even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~N","text_ar":"رَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eating;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotimaAmN","text_ar":"اِرْتِمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISh, T.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~ahu","text_ar":"رَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarum~u","text_ar":"يَرُمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~N","text_ar":"رَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayokumo biA^alobaAni Albaqari","text_ar":"عَلَيْكُمْ بِاَلْبَانِ البَقَرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_in~ahaA tarum~u mino kul~i Al$~ajari","text_ar":"فَاـِنَّهَا تَرُمُّ مِنْ كُلِّ الشَّجَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep ye to the milk of cows, for they eat of all the tress"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, S, * TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^okulu","text_ar":"تَاْكُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to one reading, it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarotam~u","text_ar":"تَرْتَمُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~ati Al$~aApu AlHa$iy$a","text_ar":"رَمَّتِ الشَّاةُ الحَشِيشَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarum~u","text_ar":"تَرُمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~N","text_ar":"رَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat, took the dry herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fodder, with its lips."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~ati Al$~aApu","text_ar":"رَمَّتِ الشَّاةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"مِنَ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Artm~t","text_ar":"ارتمّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat, ate from the land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~ati Albahomapu","text_ar":"رَمَّتِ البَهْمَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albahiymapu","text_ar":"البَهِيمَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n. as above; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Artm~t","text_ar":"ارتمّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lamb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quadruped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reached and took the branches"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with its mouth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~a rumaAmK","text_ar":"كُلَّ رُمَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yataram~amu","text_ar":"هُوَ يَتَرَمَّمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He eats every"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumaAm","text_ar":"رُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaZoma","text_ar":"العَظْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trm~m","text_ar":"ترمّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate off the flesh from the bone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aqahu","text_ar":"تَعَرَّقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he left the bone like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rim~ap","text_ar":"رِمَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: in [some of] the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taram~ama","text_ar":"تَرَمَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously explained by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaz~aqa","text_ar":"تَعَزَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [in my MS. copy, by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~afa","text_ar":"تَعَرَّفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in the CK, by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafar~aqa","text_ar":"تَفَرَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] the right reading being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aqa","text_ar":"تَعَرَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the A. (TA.) And it is said in a trad., respecting the she-cat,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA","text_ar":"وَلَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino xa$aA$i AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"مِنْ خَشَاشِ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalotuhaA turamorimu","text_ar":"اَرْسَلْتُهَا تُرَمْرِمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I did not send her"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for her to eat"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the creeping things of the earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~a AlEaZomu","text_ar":"رَمَّ العَظْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarim~u","text_ar":"يَرِمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Mgh, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~N","text_ar":"رَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rim~apN","text_ar":"رِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or both, (K, TA, [the former written in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rim~","text_ar":"رِمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiymN","text_ar":"رَمِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arm~","text_ar":"ارمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K; [but see what follows;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bone became such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rm~ap","text_ar":"رمَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, TA;) [i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became old and decayed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliYa","text_ar":"بَلِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, Mgh, Msb, K.) Accord. to IAar, one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~ato EiZaAmuhu","text_ar":"رَمَّتْ عِظَامُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aram~ato","text_ar":"اَرَمَّتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His bones became old and decayed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliyato","text_ar":"بَلِيَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but others explain"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaZomu","text_ar":"العَظْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arm~","text_ar":"ارمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"differently, as below: see 4. (T.) In the saying, mentioned in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA","text_ar":"يَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwla A@ll~`hi kayofa tuEoroDu SalaAtunaA Ealayoka waqado A^aramota","text_ar":"رَسُولَ ا@للّٰهِ كَيْفَ تُعْرْضُ صَلَاتُنَا عَلَيْكَ وَقَدْ اَرَمْتَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliyta","text_ar":"بَلِيتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O Apostle of God, how shall our blessing be offered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"addressed, to thee when thou shalt have become decayed"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the grave?], the last word is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aromamota","text_ar":"اَرْمَمْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; one of the two"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"s being rejected; like as is done in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHasota","text_ar":"اَحَسْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHosasota","text_ar":"اَحْسَسْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAth, K, * TA: [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoraDu","text_ar":"تَعْرَضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuEoraDu","text_ar":"تُعْرَضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) accord. to one relation, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aram~ata","text_ar":"اَرَمَّتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; accord. to another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramamota","text_ar":"رَمَمْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and accord. to another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^urimota","text_ar":"اُرِمْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but the first is the proper manner of relation. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ram~a AlHabolu","text_ar":"رَمَّ الحَبْلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rope became"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old and worn out"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rotten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~apN","text_ar":"رُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ragged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissundered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","Msb","K","T","TA","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n16568","headword_ar":"رُمَّةٌ","root":"rm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains of a rope after it has become ragged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissundered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of a rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is old and worn out"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rotten;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rim~apN","text_ar":"رِمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumamN","text_ar":"رُمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimamN","text_ar":"رِمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimaAmN","text_ar":"رِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aromaAmN","text_ar":"اَرْمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and they said also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN A^aromaAmN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ اَرْمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimamN","text_ar":"رِمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumamN","text_ar":"رُمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimaAmN","text_ar":"رِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN A^aromaAvN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ اَرْمَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawobN A^axolaAqN","text_ar":"ثَوْبٌ اَخْلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;] thus using the pl. as though every part [of the rope] were termed a single thing. (M.) ―         -b2-  Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTayotuhu Al$~aYo'a birum~atihi","text_ar":"اَعْطَيْتُهُ الشَّىْءَ بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave him the thing altogether:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaEa A_ilayohi Al$~aYo'a birum~atihi","text_ar":"دَفَعَ اـِلَيْهِ الشَّىْءَ بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him the thing altogether:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu birum~atihi","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it altogether:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M; and the like is said in the Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuka biAl$~aYo'i birum~tihi","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُكَ بِالشَّىْءِ بِرُمّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I brought thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have brought thee, the thing altogether:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTaAhu birum~atihi","text_ar":"اَعْطَاهُ بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave it altogether:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) originally meaning the rope that is put upon the neck of the camel: (T:) [i. e.] originating from the fact that a man gave to another a camel with a rope upon his neck: (S, K:) or from the fact that a man sold a camel with a rope upon his neck; and it was said, Give him with his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~ap","text_ar":"رُمَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or, as some say, from the bringing a captive bound with his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~ap","text_ar":"رُمَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is not a valid assertion. (M.) In all the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~um~apu","text_ar":"الرُّمَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also expl. as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljabohapu","text_ar":"الجَبْهَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but [SM says,] I have not found it in the originals from which it is derived; and may-be the right reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljumolapu","text_ar":"الجُمْلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) 'Alee said, dispraising the present world,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobaAbuhaA rimaAmN","text_ar":"اَسْبَابُهَا رِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its ties"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ropes"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old and worn out"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rotten."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aromaAmN","text_ar":"اَرْمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~apN","text_ar":"رُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] also signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last remains of herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n16569","headword_ar":"رِمَّةٌ","root":"rm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Old and decayed bones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T, S, M, Msb, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old and decayed, of bones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimamN","text_ar":"رِمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimaAmN","text_ar":"رِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) The performance of the act termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotinojaA='","text_ar":"الاِسْتِنْجَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"therewith is forbidden. (Mgh, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiymN","text_ar":"رَمِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bone in which is marrow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Freytag, from the “ Kitáb el-Addád. ”)] ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~apN","text_ar":"رُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A two-winged ant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) so accord. to Aboo-Hátim; but disallowed by ElBekree. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araDap","text_ar":"اَرَضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"woodfretter"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M, K,) in some one or more of the dialects. (M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["AA","T","S","M","Msb","K","Mgh"]}]}}